OL,3,CStockton councillor resigns over
OL,4,C'harmful' comments online
OL,6,FA Stockton councillor has resigned
OL,7,Fafter she was accused of
OL,8,F"inflammatory" and "harmful" comments
OL,9,Fposted on Facebook.
OL,11,FConservative Councillor Susan Scott,
OL,12,Fwho represents the Fairfield ward in
OL,13,FStockton, said it was her view that
OL,14,Fthe "aspiration of Muslims is to make
OL,15,Fthe whole world Muslim and they will
OL,16,Fdo whatever it takes to achieve that
OL,17,Fgoal".
