OL,3,CStockton councillor resigns over
OL,4,C'harmful' comments online
OL,6,FCllr Scott made the comments in a
OL,7,FFacebook group called 'Stockton
OL,8,FPolitics', adding: "We ignore this
OL,9,Fthreat at our peril."
OL,11,FThe Conservative group leader on
OL,12,FStockton Council, Councillor Tony
OL,13,FRiordan said she had tendered her
OL,14,Fresignation with immediate effect,
OL,15,Fwhich he had accepted.
OL,17,FCllr Riordan said: "Following a recent
OL,18,Fsocial media post by Councillor Susan
OL,19,FScott she has resigned from the
OL,20,FConservative group and Stockton
OL,21,FBorough Council with immediate effect.
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@UO]yD@TOU
