OL,6,F"It is vitally important that anyone
OL,7,Fwho posts comments on social media,
OL,8,Fparticularly those who are elected to
OL,9,Fhold public office must, always,
OL,10,Fuphold the highest of standards.
OL,12,F"The Conservative group will not
OL,13,Fcondone any behaviour that falls below
OL,14,Fthese standards and seeks to cause
OL,15,Fdivision within our communities."
OL,17,FStockton Council leader, Labour's Bob
OL,18,FCook said: "She has done the right
OL,19,Fthing and resigned.
