OL,6,F"However questions remain as to how
OL,7,Fsomebody with her views has been
OL,8,Faccepted as a Tory candidate and
OL,9,FConservative local councillor."
OL,11,FMo Waqas, chairman of Stockton Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrats, said Cllr Scott's comments
OL,13,Fwere "inflammatory" and "harmful".
OL,15,FA statement said they came at a
OL,16,Fparticularly volatile time when riots
OL,17,Fwere erupting across the UK "fuelled
OL,18,Fby misinformation and far right
OL,19,Fextremist rhetoric" and there was a
OL,20,F"dangerous trend" towards Islamophobia.
