OL,3,CStockton councillor resigns over
OL,4,C'harmful' comments online
OL,6,FIt referred to attempts to target a
OL,7,Fmosque in Hartlepool and a rise in
OL,8,Fracial tensions in Middlesbrough,
OL,9,Fleaving many Muslims scared to leave
OL,10,Ftheir homes, along with physical
OL,11,Fattacks on ethnic minorities.
OL,13,FMr Waqas, who stood as the Lib Dem
OL,14,Fcandidate for Middlesbrough and
OL,15,FThornaby East in last month's General
OL,16,FElection, said: "We struggle to
OL,17,Funderstand the logic behind such
OL,18,Fdivisive comments, especially
OL,19,Fconsidering the importance of
OL,20,Ffostering a community based on mutual
OL,21,Frespect and inclusivity.
OL,26,@xD@QOU
