OL,6,FA resident in Cllr Scott's Fairfield
OL,7,Fward, speaking before her resignation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I have many friends and
OL,9,Fneighbours who are Muslim and how can
OL,10,Fshe be expected to represent those
OL,11,Fpeople fairly when she holds such
OL,12,Fviews?"
OL,14,FThe matter had been brought to the
OL,15,Fattention of the council's monitoring
OL,16,Fofficer.
