OL,6,FA council spokeswoman confirmed a
OL,7,Fformal resignation had been received,
OL,8,Fadding: "A notice of vacancy has been
OL,9,Fpublished today and the chief
OL,10,Fexecutive of the council, who is also
OL,11,Fthe returning officer, will begin the
OL,12,Fprocess of holding a by-election in
OL,13,Fthe ward."
OL,15,FCllr Scott, who was elected in May
OL,16,Flast year, has been contacted for
OL,17,Fcomment.
